metadata.name: PROLOGUE: Last Piece of The COASIS
metadata.description:
The Coasis
Itâ€™s currently only in our memory

In the world of unknown in the digital space as big as the universe, There existed rich land of dreams called The Coasis.

Various forms of art and music coexist.
We could form the desired shape of our identity, let it disappear, or let it rebirth.

Unknown errors demolished this land into debris and pieces, and we floated around in this digital world like dust.

Guardians of The Coasis, OVN, has wandered the universe for a long time and they collected sound bites and music bits that created the lost land.

With the last piece of the Coasis land,
they returned to the real world to reconstruct it with everyone.
